Class BaseLattice<L extends BaseLattice<L>>

  • java.lang.Object

    All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseHeapDomain, BaseNonRelationalValueDomain, FunctionalLattice, InverseSetLattice, SetLattice
    public abstract class BaseLattice<L extends BaseLattice<L>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Lattice<L>
    A base implementation of the Lattice interface, handling base cases of the methods exposed by that interface. All implementers of Lattice should inherit from this class for ensuring a consistent behavior on the base cases, unless explicitly needed.
